<item>
            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-351] asyncAddEntry should not throw an exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-351</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are cases where LedgerHandle.asyncAddEntry() fails with a RuntimeException that is thrown by executor.submit(). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should better invoke the callback with a failure result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
